nd-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; line-height: 115%;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">-\r\nPersonal information when registering an account. When you register to use Subsuf’s\r\nservice, we will ask for your personal information such as name, address,\r\nemail, phone numbers to store with your account. If you choose to register with\r\nFacebook, Google or other social networking sites, we will request to access to\r\nthe personal account and may collect information such as your name, contact\r\ninformation, friends list and your favorite sites. Collecting personal\r\ninformation is essential and mandatory when you choose to use Subsuf’s service.\r\nThis helps you to avoid the risks, fraud and guarantee your rights.<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 7.5pt 0cm 7.5pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.05pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; line-height: 115%;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">-\r\nInformation when using Subsuf’s service:<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 7.5pt 0cm 7.5pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.05pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; line-height: 115%;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">&nbsp;(a) Financial transaction: When you engage in\r\nany financial transactions on Subsuf, you will be asked to provide &nbsp;information to facilitate your transaction\r\nsuch as bank accounts or other accounts of online payment gateways (Paypal), security\r\ncode, phone number and billing address.<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 7.5pt 0cm 7.5pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.05pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; line-height: 115%;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">&nbsp;(b) When you subscribe to a post, blog or\r\npromotion, advertisement, we will update &nbsp;you name and email address.<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 7.5pt 0cm 7.5pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.05pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; line-height: 115%;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">&nbsp;(c) Subsuf will also use various technologies\r\nto collect and store information such as Cookies, Log File, Web beacons ... to\r\nrecord your browser details including your IP address, browser types, the web\r\npages you visit, time you spend on the site.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></font></span><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; text-indent: 0.05pt; color: inherit;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">These\r\ntools help Subsuf track and analyze how you use the website and thereby improve\r\nour site and business</font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 7.5pt 0cm 7.5pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.05pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:\" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",\"serif\"\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 7.5pt 0cm 7.5pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.05pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; line-height: 115%;\"><font face=\"Verdana\"><b>2.\r\nHow do we use those information?</b><o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 7.5pt 0cm 7.5pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.05pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; line-height: 115%;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">-\r\nRegister, provide you our service.<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 7.5pt 0cm 7.5pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.05pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; line-height: 115%;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">-\r\nGuarantee your rights when using Subsuf’s service, and help you to avoid risks\r\nor frauds<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 7.5pt 0cm 7.5pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.05pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; line-height: 115%;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">-\r\nReview, analyze the market, customer behaviors and service quality to maintain,\r\nimprove, develop new services and also help you use our site more conveniently.<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 7.5pt 0cm 7.5pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.05pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; line-height: 115%;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">-\r\nPromote our products, services or to provide marketing, advertising\r\nand other information that you may be interested.<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 7.5pt 0cm 7.5pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.05pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; line-height: 115%;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">-\r\nCollect your feedbacks to improve your service.<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 7.5pt 0cm 7.5pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.05pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; line-height: 115%;\"><font face=\"Verdana\"><b>3.\r\nWhen do we disclose your information to third parties?</b><o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 7.5pt 0cm 7.5pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.05pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; line-height: 115%;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">We\r\nonly disclose your personal information to third parties with your consent.\r\nHowever, we may disclose your information to the following entities:<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 7.5pt 0cm 7.5pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.05pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; line-height: 115%;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">-\r\nThe contractors, service providers and business partners in the supply of\r\nSubsuf’s support services such as website management, financial transaction .... Please note that, privacy policy will comply with the policy of this third party.<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 7.5pt 0cm 7.5pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.05pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; line-height: 115%;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">-\r\nGovernment or other parties to comply with and regulations. This is to\r\nprotect the rights and property of Subsuf and associated companies.<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 7.5pt 0cm 7.5pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.05pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; line-height: 115%;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">-\r\nWe can disclose to one or more third parties the information collected about\r\nyou as part of the merger, acquisition, or transfer of any assets or business of\r\nSubsuf. Meanwhile, the security will adhere to the privacy policies of these\r\nentities.</font><font face=\"Times New Roman, serif\"><o:p></o:p></font></span></p></h2>','en'),(1,'Chính sách bảo mật','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.05pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; line-height: 115%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">Chính sách bảo mật này nhằm mục\r\nđích cung cấp cho bạn những thông tin về nguyên tắc thu thập và sử dụng thông\r\ntin cá nhân của bạn khi bạn sử dụng dịch vụ của Subsuf. <o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 7.5pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.05pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; line-height: 115%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"Verdana\">Dưới đây là những thông tin cụ thể\r\nvề chính sách bảo mật:<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin: 0cm 7.5pt 7.5pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.05pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font face=\"Verdana\"><b><span style=\"line-height: 115%;\">1.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-weight: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span></b><!--[endif]--><b><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; line-height: 115%;\">Subsuf thu thập những thông tin gì?</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; line-height: 115%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin: 0cm 7.35pt 7.5pt 21.25pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.05pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font face=\"Verdana\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; line-height: 115%;\">-<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><strong><i><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%\">Thông tin cá nhân khi đăng kí tài khoản. </span></i></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; line-height: 115%;\">Khi\r\nbạn đăng ký để sử dụng dịch vụ của Subsuf, chúng tôi sẽ yêu cầu<span class=\"apple-converted-space\">&nbsp;</span></span><a href=\"https://www.google.com/intl/vi/policies/privacy/key-terms/#toc-terms-personal-info\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; line-height: 115%;\">thông\r\ntin cá nhân</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; line-height: 115%;\"> như tên, địa chỉ, email, số điện thoại để\r\nlưu trữ với tài khoản của bạn. Nếu bạn chọn đăng kí sử dụng dịch vụ của Subsuf\r\nqua Facebook, Twitter hoặc các trang mạng xã hội khác, chúng tôi sẽ yêu cầu\r\ntruy cập vào các tài khoản cá nhân này và có thể thu thập thông tin như tên,\r\nthông tin liên lạc, danh sách bạn bè và các trang bạn yêu thích. <span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">Thu thập thông tin cá nhân được xem là yếu tố cần thiết\r\nvà bắt buộc khi bạn tham gia đăng ký, sử dụng dịch vụ của Subsuf để đảm bảo quyền\r\nlợi của chính bản thân bạn và giúp bạn tránh khỏi những rủi ro và hành vi gian\r\nlận.<o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin: 0cm 7.5pt 7.5pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.05pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font face=\"Verdana\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; line-height: 115%;\">-<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><strong><i><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;line-height:\r\n115%\">Thông tin trong quá trình sử dụng dịch vụ</span></i></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; line-height: 115%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 5pt 7.5pt 5pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.05pt; line-height: 115%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"Verdana\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-size: 13.3333px;\">(a) &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;line-height:115%\">Quá\r\ntrình giao dịch mua bán: Khi bạn tham gia bất cứ hoạt động giao dịch tài chính\r\nnào trên Subsuf, bạn sẽ được hỏi về các thông tin về tài khoản ngân hàng hoặc\r\ntài khoản của cổng thanh toán trực tuyến (Paypal, Ngân Lượng) như số tài khoản,\r\nmã bảo vệ, số điện thoại và địa chỉ thanh toán. <o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 5pt 7.5pt 5pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.05pt; line-height: 115%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"Verdana\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-size: 13.3333px;\">(b) &nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;line-height:115%\">Khi\r\nbạn đăng kí theo dõi các bài đăng, blog hoặc các thông tin về khuyến mãi, quảng\r\ncáo của Subsuf, chúng tôi sẽ cập nhật tên và địa chỉ email của bạn. <o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin: 5pt 7.5pt 5pt 21.3pt; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0.05pt; line-height: 115%; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><font face=\"Verdana\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-size: 13.3333px;\">(c) &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt;line-height:115%\">Subsuf\r\ncũng sẽ sử dụng các cô<span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\">ng cụ thu thập thông tin\r\nnhư Cookies, Log File, Web beacons… để ghi lại các thông tin trình duyệt của\r\nbạn bao gồm địa chỉ IP, loại trình duyệt, các trang web bạn truy cập, thời gian\r\nghé thăm các trang web. Các công cụ này giúp Subsuf theo dõi và phân tích cách\r\nngười dùng sử dụng website để cải tiến các tính năng của web.</span><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-right: 7.5pt; margin-left