-size: 13pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">2.</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><b><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">Purpose of Subsuf</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.3pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;line-height:normal;mso-outline-level:4\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">Subsuf is an e-commerce transaction\r\nplatform allows and creates opportunities for delivery service between users\r\nwhich related to people with cross-nation travel demand and shoppers. To use\r\nSubsuf or becoming a Traveler or Shopper, you have to be first a member of\r\nsubsuf by registering an account via Subsuf. Becoming a member, you reserve the\r\nright to accept requests on Subsuf website to buy and delver items as a Traveler.\r\nYou are also capable of sending requests to Subsuf website in order to buy\r\nitems as a Shopper.</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\nline-height:normal;mso-outline-level:4;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><b><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">3.</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><b><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">Create a Subsuf\r\naccount</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.3pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;line-height:normal;mso-outline-level:4\"><b><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">You are required to\r\nbe in the age of eight-teen (18) or above to be a member.&nbsp;</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">When register to be a\r\nmember, you shall be requested to create a profile account which contains some\r\npersonal information. After finishing the register process, you shall be\r\nrequest to confirm: (a) the provided personal information is accurate; (b) In\r\nthe case of information changing, you are subjected to adjust the information\r\nto be accurate; (c)You have read and agree to be bound by Subsuf’s term of use\r\nand Security policy.</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:21.3pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:\r\ninter-ideograph;line-height:normal;mso-outline-level:4\"><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">It is possible to create a Subsuf\r\naccount via Facebook or Google. Personal information provided to Subsuf is\r\nrequired to be accurate. Users are obligated to adjust the information in the\r\ncase of change. In the case of register via Facebook, Google, you agree to gain\r\nSubsuf the access into your Facbook profile information. &nbsp;You also agree\r\nto let Subsuf Sends information related to your Subsuf account via your\r\nFacebook and Goggle account.</span><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\r\nline-height:normal;mso-outline-level:4;vertical-align:baseline\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><b><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">4.</span></b><span style=\"font-size: 7pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp;</span><b><span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">Manage your Subsuf account</sp